OL,3,CSchool staff receive award for saving
OL,4,Cpupils from 'frenzied' glass attack
OL,6,FTwo staff members who saved school
OL,7,Fchildren in Sheffield from a glass
OL,8,Fattack have received awards for their
OL,9,Fbravery.
OL,11,FMolly Bulmer and Alicia Richards were
OL,12,Fcommended for their instant reactions
OL,13,Fto a frenzied attack on a pupil on the
OL,14,Fmorning of 1 May 2024.
OL,16,FLouis Melotte, who was 17 at the time,
OL,17,Fentered the school reception area with
OL,18,Fbroken glass hidden up his sleeve. He
OL,19,Fthen talked to receptionist Ms
OL,20,FRichards before launching into an
OL,21,Fattack on a 12-year-old pupil.
