OL,6,FMs Richards and Ms Bulmer responded
OL,7,Fwithout hesitation to apprehend
OL,8,FMelotte. Ms Bulmer managed to restrain
OL,9,Fhim, allowing the pupil and her
OL,10,Ffriends to escape.
OL,12,FMs Bulmer was then struck with the
OL,13,Fglass at least ten times. Ms Richards
OL,14,Farrived to support her and prevent
OL,15,FMelotte from getting further into the
OL,16,Fschool.
OL,18,FBoth staff members suffered minor
OL,19,Finjuries and restrained him until
OL,20,FSouth Yorkshire Police officers
OL,21,Farrived at the scene to arrest him.
