OL,3,CSchool staff receive award for saving
OL,4,Cpupils from 'frenzied' glass attack
OL,6,FDCI Knowles, from South Yorkshire
OL,7,FPolice, said: "Their actions that day
OL,8,Fprevented Melotte gaining access to
OL,9,Fthe building, allowing school staff
OL,10,Fthe time to initiate lockdown
OL,11,Fprocedures and keep all the children
OL,12,Fin their care safe from harm.
OL,14,F"I have no doubts whatsoever that it
OL,15,Fwas the actions of Ms Richards and Ms
OL,16,FBulmer that saved the community of
OL,17,FBirley from what could have been the
OL,18,Fmost unimaginable tragedy and I am
OL,19,Ftruly humbled by their courage."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
