OL,3,CSchool staff receive award for saving
OL,4,Cpupils from 'frenzied' glass attack
OL,6,FThe pair were presented with awards on
OL,7,Fbehalf of Judge Jeremy Richardson KC
OL,8,Ffor their instant reactions to the
OL,9,Fincident at Birley Academy on the
OL,10,Fmorning on 1 May 2024.
OL,12,FHe said: "You didn't stand back but
OL,13,Finstead intervened in a very
OL,14,Fcourageous manner without a thought
OL,15,Ffor your own safety. Your actions are
OL,16,Fdeserving of high praise as they were
OL,17,Fin the best tradition of education."
