OL,3,CSchool staff receive award for saving
OL,4,Cpupils from 'frenzied' glass attack
OL,6,FMelotte, of Jaunty Avenue, Sheffield,
OL,7,Fwas found guilty of three counts of
OL,8,Fattempting to cause grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm with intent following a trial at
OL,10,FSheffield Crown Court in August.
OL,12,FHe had already pleaded guilty to two
OL,13,Fcounts of wounding without intent and
OL,14,Fpossession of a sharply pointed
OL,15,Farticle on a school premises.
OL,17,FThe now 18-year-old was given a 10-
OL,18,Fyear extended sentence comprising of
OL,19,Ffive years in a young offenders
OL,20,Finstitution and an extended licence
OL,21,Fperiod of five years.
